README for shared-mime-info


IMPORTANT NOTES

    The upstream CRUX port fails to build as-is: update-mime-database.cpp
    includes <filesystem>, but GCC 7.5.0 only ships the pre-standard Filesystem
    TS (<experimental/filesystem>/std::filesystem::experimental), not std::
    filesystem, despite reporting full C++17 support.

    This overlay patches the source to use the experimental header/namespace
    and adds -lstdc++fs to LDFLAGS, since those symbols live in a separate
    library on this GCC version.
